WEBVTT

00:11.030 --> 00:17.540
[Fill Your Belly]

00:12.800 --> 00:13.930
We finally found it.

00:14.080 --> 00:15.010
Yeah, this is it.

00:15.240 --> 00:15.800
Let's go.

00:16.000 --> 00:17.000
Stop right there.

00:22.070 --> 00:23.190
Why is there someone else here?

00:23.190 --> 00:23.760
Didn't you see him?

00:23.760 --> 00:25.290
Didn't you see him just now?

00:30.670 --> 00:32.000
Put down the title deed,

00:32.240 --> 00:33.390
and I'll let you go.

00:45.600 --> 00:46.460
Not happening.

00:47.880 --> 00:49.840
I'm walking out loud and proud.

00:50.350 --> 00:51.880
Try and stop me.

01:01.560 --> 01:03.520
You darn scoundrels.

01:03.820 --> 01:05.489
Put it down now!

01:14.010 --> 01:15.480
You nosy neighbors

01:15.510 --> 01:17.240
really don't know when to quit.

01:17.840 --> 01:19.480
All lining up for death, huh?

01:19.560 --> 01:20.430
Before you go anywhere,

01:20.430 --> 01:23.039
see if my broom

01:23.039 --> 01:24.000
agrees!

01:34.789 --> 01:35.590
Get over here.

01:36.150 --> 01:36.920
I dare you.

01:37.800 --> 01:38.660
You old geezer.

01:39.000 --> 01:40.870
You run, I chase.
You're not going anywhere!

01:40.870 --> 01:41.479
Wait!

01:55.520 --> 01:56.580
Trying to run, huh?

01:57.039 --> 01:58.240
You think you can run?

01:59.710 --> 02:00.560
Are you okay?

02:00.560 --> 02:01.400
I'm not!

02:07.040 --> 02:08.080
You dare hit me?

02:08.080 --> 02:09.360
Yeah, you're exactly who I meant to hit!

02:09.360 --> 02:10.960
I... I'll teach you a lesson!

02:10.960 --> 02:12.070
For doing evil!

02:12.090 --> 02:13.420
I'll teach you a lesson!

02:14.030 --> 02:14.720
For doing evil!

02:14.720 --> 02:15.580
For doing evil!

02:15.870 --> 02:16.630
These blows don't miss.

02:16.630 --> 02:18.490
Find somewhere to hide, now!

02:28.800 --> 02:30.150
You stubborn old fool.

02:47.360 --> 02:49.630
Take that! Take that!

02:50.590 --> 02:51.360
Changyu!

02:51.360 --> 02:52.870
Changyu, Changyu, quick!

02:53.230 --> 02:56.280
[Fan]

02:53.350 --> 02:54.120
Mrs. Zhuang.

02:54.190 --> 02:55.079
Please look after Changning for me.

02:55.079 --> 02:55.590
Okay.

03:10.190 --> 03:11.740
Get lost!

03:26.710 --> 03:27.430
Miss Fan.

03:27.430 --> 03:28.360
Listen to me!

03:34.360 --> 03:35.710
I dare any of you!

03:43.680 --> 03:45.320
Quick, come on.

03:45.350 --> 03:46.120
Changyu.

03:46.650 --> 03:48.050
Stop hitting them.

03:48.430 --> 03:50.470
Zhao has beaten them half to death.

03:50.630 --> 03:51.710
If you step in,

03:51.840 --> 03:53.840
they're really not going to make it.

03:56.910 --> 03:58.270
You never learn, do you?

03:59.240 --> 04:00.150
Miss Fan.

04:00.480 --> 04:01.620
Dear Miss Fan.

04:02.470 --> 04:03.610
Please don't get the wrong idea.

04:03.610 --> 04:04.900
We came this time

04:06.120 --> 04:07.240
because we heard you're getting married.

04:07.240 --> 04:08.360
We're here to congratulate you.

04:08.360 --> 04:08.960
Yeah, that's right.

04:08.960 --> 04:10.430
W-We're here to congratulate you.

04:10.430 --> 04:12.490
We're not here to take the title deed.

04:14.960 --> 04:18.600
You call this offering congratulations,
coming armed like this?

04:18.600 --> 04:20.399
My husband was already injured,

04:20.560 --> 04:22.220
and you still ganged up on him!

04:22.430 --> 04:23.390
No, no, no!

04:23.390 --> 04:24.600
-We didn't!
-We really didn't!

04:24.600 --> 04:26.160
We didn't even lay a finger on him.

04:26.160 --> 04:27.070
W-We didn't hurt him.

04:27.070 --> 04:28.070
We didn't hit him.

04:32.510 --> 04:33.840
But you frightened him.

04:34.800 --> 04:35.770
And that's not acceptable either!

04:35.770 --> 04:37.120
Please don't. Don't.

04:44.360 --> 04:47.120
So this is your esteemed husband.

04:47.430 --> 04:48.950
We didn't know
who we were dealing with.

04:48.950 --> 04:50.020
We truly didn't.

04:50.270 --> 04:51.800
Money. Bring out the money.

04:53.310 --> 04:55.040
We really came to
offer our congratulations.

04:55.040 --> 04:56.100
Congratulations.

04:59.330 --> 05:00.460
Please spare us.

05:01.750 --> 05:02.950
That's all we've got.

05:03.630 --> 05:04.560
Please spare us.

05:05.000 --> 05:05.830
Get lost.

05:06.920 --> 05:08.560
If you dare come back
and cause trouble again,

05:08.560 --> 05:11.290
you'll deserve it
even if you get beaten to death!

05:11.310 --> 05:12.870
Let's go.

05:14.560 --> 05:16.120
Leave at once! Get lost!

05:16.480 --> 05:18.410
-Well done!
-Well done! Well done!

05:20.210 --> 05:21.250
Are you okay?

05:23.220 --> 05:24.880
So they did hurt you after all.

05:25.630 --> 05:26.190
I'll go kill them.

05:26.190 --> 05:27.390
They're not to blame.

05:28.390 --> 05:29.480
Then who's to blame?

05:29.480 --> 05:30.410
Me. I'm to blame.

05:31.600 --> 05:32.630
I sat on him.

05:32.950 --> 05:33.830
I was part of it too.

05:33.830 --> 05:34.560
Me too.

05:34.560 --> 05:35.560
And me.

05:39.190 --> 05:40.159
-Alright.
-Come on.

05:40.159 --> 05:42.760
-Here we are. Be careful.
-Excuse me. Make way.

05:42.950 --> 05:45.750
Your uncle is to blame. He's so clumsy.

05:45.950 --> 05:47.070
I was just out buying groceries,

05:47.070 --> 05:48.920
and he hurt him by sitting on him.

05:48.920 --> 05:50.680
Just when he was recovering.

05:50.830 --> 05:52.360
Actually, he survived
thanks to Mr. Zhao's help.

05:52.360 --> 05:53.760
I should be thanking you.

05:54.210 --> 05:55.880
Mrs. Zhao, you guys go rest.

05:56.240 --> 05:57.480
I'll take care of Yan Zheng.

05:57.480 --> 05:58.120
Okay.

05:58.430 --> 06:00.600
I'll go make some dishes
to treat everyone.

06:00.600 --> 06:01.240
Alright.

06:01.240 --> 06:02.040
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

06:02.040 --> 06:02.720
Go outside.

06:04.360 --> 06:06.360
Yan Zheng, give me your hand.

06:08.810 --> 06:10.320
Zhao, come out here.

06:10.750 --> 06:11.510
What for?

06:12.410 --> 06:13.530
What do you think?

06:13.560 --> 06:14.990
But I haven't checked his pulse yet.

06:14.990 --> 06:15.920
Forget about it.

06:15.930 --> 06:16.990
Can't you read the room?

06:16.990 --> 06:18.310
Read what room?

06:32.620 --> 06:34.420
The wound on your back reopened.

06:34.650 --> 06:36.250
There's a large bloodstain.

06:36.800 --> 06:37.860
It needs cleaning.

06:38.270 --> 06:39.750
I-I'll do it myself.

06:39.770 --> 06:40.450
Let me.

06:52.440 --> 06:54.740
You beat those men, didn't you?

06:56.159 --> 06:57.290
This wound of yours—

06:57.600 --> 06:59.040
even if Mr. Zhao sat on it,

06:59.360 --> 07:01.420
it wouldn't have torn open like this.

07:02.160 --> 07:03.360
You must have fought.

07:04.630 --> 07:05.890
With a build like that,

07:06.310 --> 07:07.390
it's obvious that

07:09.270 --> 07:11.070
you're trained in martial arts.

07:23.730 --> 07:25.260
I used to be an armed escort.

07:25.760 --> 07:27.090
I traveled all over,

07:28.010 --> 07:30.400
and just picked up some fighting skills
for self-defense.

07:30.400 --> 07:32.200
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

07:36.630 --> 07:37.430
No wonder.

07:38.680 --> 07:40.750
My father used to be an armed escort too.

07:40.750 --> 07:42.950
He also had many old wounds like yours.

07:43.100 --> 07:43.960
Being an escort

07:44.750 --> 07:46.950
is truly a life-threatening business.

07:51.500 --> 07:52.350
Bear with it.

07:56.270 --> 07:57.430
So you were wounded

07:58.070 --> 07:59.659
by bandits at Huchakou

07:59.720 --> 08:00.630
as well?

08:05.310 --> 08:06.040
Yes.

08:09.330 --> 08:11.460
There's nothing valuable in our home.

08:11.480 --> 08:12.980
If they wanted to smash things, let them.

08:12.980 --> 08:14.120
Why did you step in?

08:16.390 --> 08:17.720
If I hadn't stepped in,

08:19.480 --> 08:21.010
they would have taken this.

08:26.450 --> 08:30.170
[Deed of House Sale]

08:46.200 --> 08:47.960
So you stepped in

08:48.020 --> 08:49.150
for this title deed?

09:18.320 --> 09:19.090
Thanks a lot.

10:51.470 --> 10:56.370
[Pursuit of Jade]

10:56.450 --> 10:59.040
[Episode 4]

11:00.200 --> 11:02.510
When I swung my broom today,

11:02.790 --> 11:04.000
they all fell.

11:05.000 --> 11:07.120
Whoever I touched went down.

11:07.830 --> 11:08.890
No wonder they say,

11:08.900 --> 11:10.820
even a rabbit bites when cornered.

11:10.820 --> 11:11.870
If we hadn't fought,

11:11.870 --> 11:13.320
how would we know we were so capable?

11:13.320 --> 11:14.270
Exactly.

11:14.760 --> 11:15.560
You gentlemen

11:15.560 --> 11:17.480
are the Gods of War of Xigu Lane.

11:17.480 --> 11:18.910
-That's right. Come on.
-Of course.

11:18.910 --> 11:20.130
Cheers.

11:20.160 --> 11:21.200
Drink up.

11:24.330 --> 11:27.390
If you ask me, we're no worse than
that Marquis of Wu'an.

11:27.400 --> 11:28.280
Don't you agree?

11:28.280 --> 11:29.280
Of course.

11:30.830 --> 11:31.430
I agree.

11:34.570 --> 11:35.260
It's just

11:36.040 --> 11:38.270
you're a bit weak, kid.

11:38.290 --> 11:41.020
You got injured just because
I sat on you for a bit.

11:41.390 --> 11:43.790
Changyu, you should nourish him properly.

11:44.990 --> 11:45.870
Uncle,

11:45.890 --> 11:48.150
he's only like this
because his old injuries haven't healed.

11:48.150 --> 11:50.770
Come on, let's have a drink.

11:51.390 --> 11:53.960
Don't drink alcohol. Have tea instead.

11:54.280 --> 11:54.790
Have some tea.

11:54.790 --> 11:56.720
You care so much about your husband?

11:56.720 --> 12:00.180
It's fine. A little wine won't hurt.
It improves circulation.

12:00.270 --> 12:01.000
Zhao!

12:01.240 --> 12:02.870
Why are you making a fuss here?

12:02.870 --> 12:04.390
He just recovered. He can't drink.

12:04.390 --> 12:05.270
You think everyone's as reckless as you?

12:05.270 --> 12:07.200
-Go over there.
-Zhao. Come on, come drink over here.

12:07.200 --> 12:08.020
Let's drink.

12:08.050 --> 12:11.120
Changyu, did Fan Daniu
really file a lawsuit?

12:11.720 --> 12:13.320
Is he really that shameless?

12:16.030 --> 12:17.910
How about we hire a lawyer?

12:18.790 --> 12:20.910
Hiring a lawyer would be too expensive.

12:20.910 --> 12:22.170
What should we do then?

12:22.960 --> 12:25.390
How about talking to Song Yan?

12:26.140 --> 12:28.950
He's the only scholar in our Xigu Lane
after all.

12:28.980 --> 12:31.960
Even officials can't make
a provincial candidate kneel.

12:31.960 --> 12:34.590
He can surely help you
with the lawsuit, Changyu.

12:34.590 --> 12:36.660
Changyu won't ask a bad guy for help.

12:37.790 --> 12:38.870
Changning is right.

12:38.870 --> 12:40.270
We won't ask that ingrate for help.

12:40.270 --> 12:42.140
Right, let's not talk about that ingrate.

12:42.140 --> 12:43.850
Come on. Let's have a drink.

12:43.880 --> 12:45.280
Come on, buddy, drink up.

12:45.750 --> 12:46.270
Let's drink.

12:46.270 --> 12:46.750
Cheers.

12:46.790 --> 12:48.190
This wine is really good.

12:48.240 --> 12:48.970
Don't worry.

12:49.600 --> 12:50.400
I'll help you.

12:52.120 --> 12:52.750
You?

13:02.510 --> 13:03.340
This is everything.

13:03.340 --> 13:05.240
These were used by my mother before.

13:05.240 --> 13:06.240
Make do with them.

13:08.000 --> 13:09.330
I'll write down
the entire response process

13:09.330 --> 13:11.060
and the proper legal phrasing.

13:11.330 --> 13:12.520
Memorize it,

13:12.760 --> 13:15.630
and you'll pass the hearing
without trouble.

13:15.500 --> 13:17.680
[Household Statutes,
Legal Code of Great Yin]

13:16.030 --> 13:17.480
You know how to write?

13:17.890 --> 13:19.390
And you even have knowledge of this?

13:19.390 --> 13:21.080
I've traveled far and seen much,

13:21.080 --> 13:22.610
so I naturally picked it up.

13:34.140 --> 13:34.960
What's wrong?

13:38.360 --> 13:39.720
I used to think

13:40.430 --> 13:43.360
Song Yan was the most formidable person
in the world.

13:43.360 --> 13:45.440
I never imagined you'd be
even more impressive—

13:45.440 --> 13:46.840
not only skilled in martial arts,

13:46.840 --> 13:48.500
but also able to write so well.

13:51.050 --> 13:52.450
Is he the provincial candidate

13:52.450 --> 13:54.200
who refused to help you

13:54.850 --> 13:57.450
even though Mrs. Zhao
shouted herself hoarse?

13:58.720 --> 14:00.920
Why don't you go to court on behalf of me?

14:00.960 --> 14:02.720
According to the Legal Code of Great Yin,

14:02.720 --> 14:05.400
only the head of the household
can appear in court.

14:05.400 --> 14:06.530
I'm not the head of the household,

14:06.530 --> 14:07.580
so I cannot go.

14:08.440 --> 14:11.000
You're really putting me on the spot.

14:13.490 --> 14:14.620
It's almost my turn.

14:14.960 --> 14:15.600
Silence.

14:17.840 --> 14:20.790
Who is the petitioner below?
And what case do you present?

14:20.790 --> 14:21.550
State it now.

14:22.670 --> 14:23.870
You look so imposing.

14:23.910 --> 14:25.360
You look so imposing.

14:32.550 --> 14:33.840
Your Honor,

14:34.960 --> 14:36.150
I am Fan Changyu,

14:36.840 --> 14:37.910
and I'm here for...

14:38.260 --> 14:38.930
My house.

14:39.860 --> 14:40.840
Are your parents alive?

14:40.840 --> 14:41.750
Both are dead.

14:42.260 --> 14:43.840
According to the Legal Code of Great Yin，

14:43.840 --> 14:44.930
if a household has no male heir,

14:44.930 --> 14:46.150
the house goes to the next of kin.

14:46.150 --> 14:47.360
If the older brother dies,
the younger succeeds.

14:47.360 --> 14:49.030
-And if the younger brother dies...
-That's nonsense!

14:49.030 --> 14:50.480
That's nonsense.

14:52.910 --> 14:54.030
For causing a disturbance in court,

14:54.030 --> 14:54.960
you, Changning,

14:55.510 --> 14:56.320
are to be flogged 10 times.

14:56.320 --> 14:57.320
Got it.

14:58.830 --> 15:00.570
One. Two...

15:00.630 --> 15:01.750
You're serious?

15:05.360 --> 15:06.630
Your Honor.

15:07.910 --> 15:09.910
According to the Legal Code of Great Yin,

15:09.910 --> 15:12.870
specifically Article 17
of Extinction of a Household Circle,

15:12.870 --> 15:14.390
when a household is extinct,
circle circle inherit,

15:14.390 --> 15:15.550
and when there's a circle,
a circle makes the choice.

15:15.550 --> 15:15.910
Stop.

15:15.910 --> 15:16.510
Circle...

15:16.790 --> 15:19.790
Extinction of a Household Circle?
What's a "circle"?

15:21.150 --> 15:23.120
I can never remember the characters.

15:23.120 --> 15:24.390
So my mother told me

15:25.030 --> 15:25.910
to draw a circle
for each character I don't know.

15:25.910 --> 15:27.140
I'm used to reading like this.

15:27.140 --> 15:28.680
[Article 17, Extinction of a Household Section,
Household Statutes, Legal Code of Great Yin]

15:30.000 --> 15:31.730
I really can't remember these.

15:31.870 --> 15:32.730
How about this?

15:33.960 --> 15:34.910
Let's find a sack

15:34.960 --> 15:37.160
and kidnap Fan Daniu. What do you think?

15:38.320 --> 15:39.030
What then?

15:39.360 --> 15:40.270
Mr. Wang said

15:40.630 --> 15:42.440
if he's not there on the day of the trial,

15:42.440 --> 15:43.640
the case won't count.

15:51.120 --> 15:52.480
Since it happened once,

15:52.700 --> 15:54.150
it will happen again.

15:55.000 --> 15:55.870
Why not

15:56.500 --> 15:58.050
just kill him

16:00.330 --> 16:01.800
and be done with it?

16:07.230 --> 16:10.090
K-Killing is against the law.

16:11.000 --> 16:12.120
L-Let's not.

16:16.210 --> 16:18.320
Since you can't bear to be that ruthless,

16:18.320 --> 16:20.390
you'll have to suffer through it yourself.

16:20.390 --> 16:21.250
Keep reciting.

16:24.290 --> 16:27.550
Extinction of a Household Section,
Household Statutes, Legal Code of Great Yin.

16:27.550 --> 16:28.870
Article 17:

16:29.000 --> 16:31.200
"In cases of household extinctions…"

16:34.030 --> 16:35.480
Don't be mad.

16:35.910 --> 16:37.270
Your health comes first.

16:37.270 --> 16:38.400
I'll keep reciting.

16:38.840 --> 16:39.500
Never mind.

16:41.030 --> 16:42.790
Just recite this Seven-Step Poem.

16:42.790 --> 16:45.010
Laws are ultimately grounded in reason,

16:45.010 --> 16:47.050
so this might be more persuasive.

16:48.030 --> 16:51.690
Magistrate Cui is a double-ranked
scholar-official, after all.

16:52.150 --> 16:53.410
What Seven-Step Poem?

16:54.910 --> 16:56.240
"Boiling beans by burning the beanstalks.

16:56.240 --> 16:57.670
The beans are sobbing inside the pot.

16:57.670 --> 16:58.880
Both of them were born from the same root.

16:58.880 --> 17:00.360
Why rush to torment each other?"

17:00.360 --> 17:01.490
What does that mean?

17:01.670 --> 17:04.599
It speaks of boiling beans
with beanstalks for fuel,

17:04.630 --> 17:07.349
a metaphor for the deadly strife
between brothers of the same father.

17:07.349 --> 17:10.440
By extension, it condemns Fan Daniu
for abusing his brother's daughter,

17:10.440 --> 17:12.240
an act devoid of kinship and morality.

17:12.240 --> 17:13.300
That's brilliant.

17:15.569 --> 17:18.550
It's like this poem was originally
written for Fan Daniu.

17:18.550 --> 17:19.880
He's not worthy of that.

17:24.710 --> 17:25.720
What does "Fu" mean?

17:25.720 --> 17:26.240
Pot.

17:28.069 --> 17:30.600
"Same root" must mean
having the same father.

17:32.430 --> 17:33.690
What about "torment"?

17:34.030 --> 17:36.050
Is it a cooking method?

17:36.110 --> 17:38.270
It's a metaphor for killing.

17:42.240 --> 17:42.960
Got it.

17:44.510 --> 17:45.510
You really got it?

17:50.830 --> 17:53.310
Boiling beans by burning the beanpoles.

17:54.350 --> 17:55.400
The beans

17:56.880 --> 17:58.200
in the pot cry out:

17:59.400 --> 18:01.720
"we share the same father,

18:01.720 --> 18:04.590
so why kill me first?"

18:11.510 --> 18:12.510
Is it wrong?

18:15.440 --> 18:16.900
I wouldn't say it's wrong.

18:18.270 --> 18:19.790
Your Honor!

18:19.790 --> 18:22.440
Your Honor!

18:26.160 --> 18:29.070
Boiling beans by burning the beanpoles.

18:29.070 --> 18:31.200
The beans in the pot cry out:

18:31.880 --> 18:34.110
"we share the same father,

18:34.110 --> 18:36.680
so why kill me first?"

18:49.330 --> 18:53.220
[Xigu Lane]

18:49.510 --> 18:51.920
Boiling beans by burning the beanpoles.

18:51.920 --> 18:54.510
The beans in the pot cry out.

18:55.150 --> 18:57.400
"we share the same father,

18:57.960 --> 19:01.000
so why kill me first?"

19:02.400 --> 19:05.110
Your Honor!

19:05.350 --> 19:09.880
Your Honor!

19:11.350 --> 19:14.000
Your Honor!

19:22.680 --> 19:24.370
Yan, where are you going?

19:27.810 --> 19:29.560
I'm just tired from studying.

19:29.790 --> 19:30.990
I want to go for a walk.

19:40.400 --> 19:42.550
You still have the metropolitan exam

19:42.580 --> 19:44.380
and the palace exam ahead of you.

19:45.200 --> 19:47.280
Don't get any foolish ideas.

19:52.570 --> 19:53.090
Okay.

20:02.600 --> 20:04.730
Boiling beans...

20:55.600 --> 20:56.320
Mother.

21:02.750 --> 21:03.680
Mother.

21:05.880 --> 21:07.010
I'm so tired.

21:56.490 --> 21:57.890
Did I wake you?

21:58.020 --> 22:00.510
I fell asleep on your hand just now?

22:05.360 --> 22:07.360
You must be sleepy from reading too.

22:09.430 --> 22:10.860
I totally understand.

22:14.780 --> 22:16.170
Why did the lamp go out?

22:16.190 --> 22:17.720
I'll go find a fire starter.

22:20.370 --> 22:22.630
It's so late. Who's knocking at the door?

22:27.400 --> 22:28.290
Song Yan?

22:28.660 --> 22:29.370
Why are you here...

22:29.370 --> 22:30.230
Let me in first.

22:30.250 --> 22:31.710
Don't let my mother see me.

22:32.770 --> 22:33.450
I have...

22:35.190 --> 22:35.910
Have what?

22:44.850 --> 22:45.480
Changyu.

22:46.350 --> 22:47.480
I'm risking the crime of
disobeying my elders

22:47.480 --> 22:48.850
and committing a great offense
to come here

22:48.850 --> 22:50.380
and help you keep this home.

22:51.270 --> 22:51.960
What?

22:52.830 --> 22:53.830
A few days ago,

22:54.030 --> 22:55.240
I thought for a long time

22:55.240 --> 22:57.240
and finally came up with a solution.

22:58.590 --> 22:59.680
I came to tell you

23:00.460 --> 23:02.920
that I'm willing to take you
as my concubine.

23:07.630 --> 23:09.500
Are you out of your mind?

23:09.530 --> 23:11.060
Don't celebrate too early.

23:11.170 --> 23:12.930
I can only try to beg the Magistrate

23:12.930 --> 23:14.420
to grant me a special dispensation.

23:14.420 --> 23:16.160
Hopefully, with my status
as a provincial candidate,

23:16.160 --> 23:18.160
the Magistrate will do me this favor.

23:18.160 --> 23:20.560
This way, you can keep your house

23:20.580 --> 23:22.580
and get the title you've wished for.

23:24.730 --> 23:25.530
Song Yan.

23:26.680 --> 23:28.680
You think just because I'm a butcher girl,

23:28.680 --> 23:31.250
and you're lowering yourself
to take me as a concubine,

23:31.250 --> 23:33.120
I should be thanking you, right?

23:33.550 --> 23:34.880
That's not what I meant.

23:35.370 --> 23:36.610
I just never expected

23:37.190 --> 23:38.420
that for this house,

23:38.830 --> 23:40.240
you would act so rashly

23:40.570 --> 23:42.730
and give yourself to
a crippled refugee from Chongzhou.

23:42.730 --> 23:43.860
A crippled refugee?

23:44.160 --> 23:44.720
Yes.

23:47.150 --> 23:48.810
Song Yan, I'm really curious.

23:50.210 --> 23:52.510
What gives you the right
to look down on him like that?

23:52.510 --> 23:54.110
Even setting aside the fact that he's both
learned and skilled in martial arts,

23:54.110 --> 23:54.860
educated and reasonable,

23:54.860 --> 23:55.680
just in terms of looks alone,

23:55.680 --> 23:57.340
Yan Zheng's 10 times better than you.

23:57.340 --> 23:58.410
Most importantly,

23:59.250 --> 24:01.140
he knows how to appreciate
what others do for him.

24:01.140 --> 24:02.810
He understands my difficulties

24:02.810 --> 24:04.940
and is willing to marry into my family.

24:05.270 --> 24:06.640
Even when he was hurt,

24:06.670 --> 24:08.230
he still stood up for me

24:08.880 --> 24:10.410
and helped me seek justice.

24:10.740 --> 24:11.740
Such devotion—

24:12.960 --> 24:15.160
isn't it 1,000 times better than yours?

24:15.640 --> 24:18.580
You're just unwilling to let go now

24:19.170 --> 24:22.120
and want to earn a good reputation
in the neighborhood,

24:22.120 --> 24:23.730
so you had no choice but to come here.

24:23.730 --> 24:24.420
Song Yan.

24:25.160 --> 24:26.560
You just can't miss out on

24:27.120 --> 24:28.830
any good thing in this world, can you?

24:28.830 --> 24:29.920
It's not like that.

24:30.050 --> 24:31.750
My feelings for you are sincere.

24:31.750 --> 24:33.300
I, Song Yan, hold your hand now,

24:33.300 --> 24:34.560
and swear to Heaven...

24:37.180 --> 24:37.620
I...

24:42.730 --> 24:43.660
Who are you?

24:44.480 --> 24:45.410
Who am I, you ask?

24:51.330 --> 24:52.600
The crippled refugee.

24:57.600 --> 24:59.090
I think of you every night,

25:00.030 --> 25:01.770
and this is how little womanly virtue
you have?

25:01.770 --> 25:03.060
Who are you to me?

25:03.240 --> 25:05.150
Why should I observe any womanly virtue?

25:05.150 --> 25:07.110
You've disregarded all sense of
decorum and morality!

25:07.110 --> 25:08.550
It's simply scandalous!

25:08.740 --> 25:09.810
According to the Legal Code of Great Yin,

25:09.810 --> 25:10.810
those who commit adultery are guilty of
fornication and shall receive 80 lashes!

25:10.810 --> 25:12.960
According to the Legal Code of Great Yin,

25:12.960 --> 25:15.400
your breaking into a private residence
at night counts as burglary,

25:15.400 --> 25:17.000
and death would be deserved.

25:17.120 --> 25:18.340
See for yourself.

25:21.390 --> 25:22.840
This is my husband,

25:23.690 --> 25:26.160
the man lawfully married to
me, Fan Changyu.

25:31.750 --> 25:32.680
You two...

25:32.930 --> 25:34.530
You two are just shameless!

25:34.720 --> 25:36.030
Shameless!

25:37.090 --> 25:39.700
To commit such acts against public morals—

25:40.180 --> 25:41.830
this is simply scandalous!

25:59.830 --> 26:01.830
Why did I kiss him?

26:03.070 --> 26:06.200
If I scared him so much that
he won't marry into my family,

26:06.630 --> 26:09.440
wouldn't I be losing a great deal
for a small gain?

26:34.910 --> 26:37.110
It's all that bastard Song Yan's fault.

26:38.170 --> 26:39.350
Bastard.

26:40.180 --> 26:42.180
Bastard. Bastard. Bastard.

26:53.330 --> 26:55.460
What on earth was that woman thinking?

26:55.960 --> 27:00.300
[Only My Virtue is Fragrant]

26:56.560 --> 26:58.960
All for that pathetic
matrilocal husband?

27:14.780 --> 27:16.850
Mrs. Zhao, where's Mr. Zhao?

27:16.880 --> 27:17.880
He went to town.

27:27.990 --> 27:29.250
Mr. Zhao, you're back.

27:29.710 --> 27:31.770
Mrs. Zhao, I need to go out for a bit.

27:32.890 --> 27:33.420
Changyu.

27:33.430 --> 27:34.080
Mr. Zhao.

27:38.540 --> 27:39.550
This young couple...

27:39.550 --> 27:42.360
Why are they acting like
they're avoiding each other?

27:42.360 --> 27:45.110
Brides get nervous before the wedding.

27:45.200 --> 27:47.340
Even though Changyu has a boyish nature,

27:47.340 --> 27:48.690
she gets shy too.

27:49.290 --> 27:51.440
So you were also shy before marrying me?

27:51.440 --> 27:52.240
Shy?

27:52.420 --> 27:54.950
-I didn't even know who to cry to!
-Look at you.

27:55.440 --> 27:56.240
Yan Zheng.

27:56.310 --> 27:58.350
Yan Zheng, you're awake.

27:59.070 --> 28:00.350
Changyu just went out.

28:00.370 --> 28:01.200
I know.

28:02.210 --> 28:03.480
I need to talk to you about something,
Mr. Zhao.

28:03.480 --> 28:04.630
I want to talk to you too.

28:04.630 --> 28:05.390
Come on.

28:05.680 --> 28:06.210
This way.

28:07.400 --> 28:08.200
Be careful.

28:10.470 --> 28:12.510
Those essays you wrote

28:13.200 --> 28:14.960
can sell for so much money?

28:16.360 --> 28:17.540
Is this a lot?

28:17.900 --> 28:19.490
Twenty taels isn't a lot?

28:19.890 --> 28:22.890
I almost thought the bookshop owner
had lost his mind.

28:25.040 --> 28:27.760
[Wuqi has arrived at
Lin'an Four Seasons Bookshop]

28:27.850 --> 28:30.450
What kind of divine calligraphy
did you write?

28:32.990 --> 28:35.160
I've traveled a lot and seen much.

28:35.200 --> 28:37.800
I just casually wrote some nonsense
to bluff people.

28:37.800 --> 28:38.750
I didn't expect

28:38.770 --> 28:40.900
the bookshop owner to actually buy it.

28:41.540 --> 28:43.740
That's pure profit.

28:44.140 --> 28:46.340
Write a few more. I'll sell them for you.

28:47.890 --> 28:49.760
I was only imitating the masters.

28:50.030 --> 28:52.440
If I write more, I might be exposed.

28:52.470 --> 28:53.730
It's not appropriate.

28:54.680 --> 28:56.900
Right, right. Can't be showy.

28:57.700 --> 28:59.370
But writing once in a while

28:59.560 --> 29:01.820
would make enough for a year's expenses.

29:03.090 --> 29:05.950
This little bit of silver
is enough for a whole year?

29:06.330 --> 29:07.880
For a humble household,

29:07.910 --> 29:09.830
if you budget carefully,

29:09.860 --> 29:11.400
it's even enough for 2 or 3 years.

29:11.400 --> 29:13.470
It seems I miscalculated after all.

29:15.510 --> 29:17.160
About me selling essays,

29:17.400 --> 29:19.220
please help me keep it a secret, Mr. Zhao.

29:19.220 --> 29:20.130
Don't tell anyone.

29:20.130 --> 29:20.930
I understand.

29:21.350 --> 29:22.760
I'm discreet.

29:22.790 --> 29:24.520
I know how to keep my mouth shut.

29:26.140 --> 29:27.310
That little fool

29:27.880 --> 29:30.700
actually got herself a husband
who knows how to make money.

29:30.700 --> 29:34.550
Her hard times are over now.
Truly blessed.

29:53.630 --> 29:54.460
Changyu.

29:54.670 --> 29:55.680
Mrs. Zhao.

29:55.700 --> 29:57.500
What took you so long?

29:58.030 --> 29:59.960
Come and see who's waiting for you.

30:00.200 --> 30:01.560
Mrs. Chen, you're here.

30:01.880 --> 30:03.150
Changyu.

30:05.060 --> 30:06.320
Open it and take a look.

30:09.320 --> 30:10.510
Come on, open it.

30:29.030 --> 30:29.590
This...

30:31.360 --> 30:32.160
For me?

30:34.200 --> 30:37.130
Didn't you say you were only making one
for the groom?

30:37.290 --> 30:39.490
Girls always side with their husbands.

30:39.850 --> 30:41.630
I deliberately saved some fabric

30:41.630 --> 30:43.390
and borrowed some scraps

30:43.420 --> 30:43.990
to make

30:44.230 --> 30:45.570
a set for you too.

30:46.320 --> 30:47.150
Thank you so much.

30:47.150 --> 30:48.220
You're welcome.

30:48.640 --> 30:50.050
So pretty.

30:50.570 --> 30:51.330
Look.

30:51.360 --> 30:52.350
It's truly pretty.

30:52.350 --> 30:53.680
So pretty.

30:56.900 --> 30:57.910
What is this?

31:05.270 --> 31:06.960
What, you don't like it?

31:09.680 --> 31:10.640
I do.

31:12.010 --> 31:13.910
But you've embroidered
such beautiful flowers—

31:13.910 --> 31:15.510
who's even going to see them?

31:15.900 --> 31:17.750
It's not for you to see.

31:19.860 --> 31:22.070
As long as your husband likes it.

31:22.090 --> 31:23.490
So this is for him to wear?

31:26.320 --> 31:27.890
My silly girl.

31:28.780 --> 31:31.780
You're wearing it for him to see
on your wedding night.

31:36.290 --> 31:37.440
Mrs. Zhao!

31:37.460 --> 31:38.840
Alright, alright.

31:55.470 --> 31:57.950
Boiling beans by burning the beanstalks.

31:58.030 --> 32:01.430
The beans sob secretly in the pot.

32:02.400 --> 32:04.650
We share the same father.

32:04.720 --> 32:07.150
Why rush to torment each other?

32:10.020 --> 32:12.780
Boiling beans by burning the beanstalks.

32:15.240 --> 32:18.650
The beans weep loudly in the pot.

32:27.910 --> 32:28.430
Oh no.

32:28.450 --> 32:31.750
-Boiling beans by burning the beanstalks.
-I shouldn't have hidden it under the bed.

32:31.750 --> 32:35.240
The beans weep loudly in the pot.

32:37.400 --> 32:39.400
We share the same father.

32:40.550 --> 32:43.030
Why rush to torment each other?

32:49.330 --> 32:50.820
Why are you here?

32:52.860 --> 32:56.320
Didn't you ask me to come and
try on the wedding suit yesterday?

32:59.160 --> 33:00.780
But our wedding outfits

33:01.350 --> 33:02.950
are with Mrs. Zhao.

33:08.760 --> 33:10.360
Why is she sitting on the bed?

33:22.780 --> 33:24.490
Why is he sitting next to me?

33:31.920 --> 33:33.400
Let's go try them on together then.

33:33.400 --> 33:34.280
Sure.

33:37.730 --> 33:38.790
Let's go together.

33:39.050 --> 33:39.640
Let's go.

33:45.820 --> 33:46.630
Let's go.

33:47.030 --> 33:47.790
Let's go.

33:48.440 --> 33:50.030
Why isn't he moving?

33:50.480 --> 33:51.960
Did he see it?

33:52.890 --> 33:55.050
Where's the box? Why can't I feel it?

33:56.400 --> 33:57.760
-Have you finished reciting it?
-Are you done with your business?

33:57.760 --> 33:58.970
R-Reciting?

33:59.810 --> 34:00.490
I...

34:01.360 --> 34:02.410
Where was I?

34:02.430 --> 34:03.960
We share the same father...

34:06.930 --> 34:09.190
Both of them were born from the same root.

34:18.010 --> 34:19.139
I'll get going then.

34:26.179 --> 34:27.710
She probably didn't see it.

34:38.139 --> 34:39.870
I'll give it to her another day.

34:48.810 --> 34:49.960
He probably didn't see it.

34:49.960 --> 34:53.159
He definitely didn't see it.
Didn't see it, didn't see it.

34:54.100 --> 34:56.120
So embarrassing.

34:57.000 --> 34:58.120
What should I do?

35:01.710 --> 35:07.730
[Happiness]

35:07.840 --> 35:10.630
[Fill Your Belly]

35:11.240 --> 35:15.650
[Happiness]

35:25.960 --> 35:27.280
It's so lively.

35:28.960 --> 35:31.110
Today is Changyu's big day.

35:31.150 --> 35:33.150
Make sure you get the rituals right.

35:33.160 --> 35:35.800
Don't worry. I know you're an expert.

35:35.820 --> 35:37.450
But today, you're the host.

35:37.480 --> 35:40.340
Just relax and drink the wedding tea.
I've got this.

35:46.680 --> 35:48.950
Are you saying that matrilocal husband
is ugly,

35:48.950 --> 35:50.720
and he's a cripple?

35:51.510 --> 35:52.820
If he's not ugly or crippled,

35:52.820 --> 35:55.170
who would choose to be
a matrilocal husband nowadays?

35:55.170 --> 35:57.170
Granny Kang, it's a joyful day.

35:57.200 --> 35:58.280
Watch your tongue.

35:58.930 --> 35:59.990
She's got so much to say.

35:59.990 --> 36:01.200
Why is she here too?

36:01.400 --> 36:04.540
She's a distant relative of
the Fan family. Can't be helped.

36:04.540 --> 36:07.370
The Fan family's son-in-law is coming out!

36:15.330 --> 36:16.560
What did I tell you?

36:16.580 --> 36:18.980
Look, if he's not missing any limbs,

36:19.010 --> 36:21.070
why would he be a matrilocal husband?

36:32.720 --> 36:33.980
I, Song Yan,

36:34.010 --> 36:36.870
am here specifically
to offer my congratulations.

36:38.460 --> 36:39.900
What are you doing here again?

36:39.900 --> 36:40.500
Changyu.

36:41.460 --> 36:43.120
I'll give you one more chance.

36:43.520 --> 36:45.150
If you are willing to be my concubine,

36:45.150 --> 36:47.680
I'll keep my vow and take you in
as a concubine.

36:47.970 --> 36:48.870
As a concubine?

36:48.920 --> 36:50.540
That is truly disgusting.

36:50.810 --> 36:52.840
Aren't you just trying to disgust Changyu
on purpose?

36:52.840 --> 36:55.770
Exactly. Aren't you just trying to
disgust Changyu?

36:57.430 --> 36:59.690
This is the token of love Changyu gave me.

37:00.250 --> 37:02.840
But now that
she's become only like a sister to me,

37:02.840 --> 37:05.050
it naturally should be passed on to
this matrilocal husband.

37:05.050 --> 37:07.400
I was only 6
when I gave you that clay doll.

37:07.420 --> 37:08.960
How does that count as a token of love?

37:08.960 --> 37:10.850
You still remember things from
when you were 6.

37:10.850 --> 37:13.580
It shows you've never let go of this
in your heart.

37:16.810 --> 37:17.950
Don't make me slap you.

37:17.950 --> 37:21.590
My childhood sweetheart is getting married.
How can I not bring a gift?

37:21.590 --> 37:23.010
Fan family's matrilocal husband.

37:23.010 --> 37:25.420
Will you accept this gift or not?

37:44.690 --> 37:48.820
♪ In the east wind,
flowers bloom at night ♪

37:50.220 --> 37:52.820
♪ Blowing down the stars like rain ♪

37:55.400 --> 37:57.570
♪ Fine horses and carved carriages
fill the fragrant streets ♪

37:58.180 --> 37:59.990
♪ The phoenix flute resounds ♪

38:00.670 --> 38:01.720
♪ The jade pot light revolves ♪

38:02.170 --> 38:05.700
♪ A night of fish-and-dragon dances ♪

38:06.120 --> 38:16.020
♪ In gold-thread dress,
with moth or willow ornaments ♪

38:06.330 --> 38:07.400
Those looks.

38:07.420 --> 38:10.030
No wonder Changyu said
she wasn't losing out.

38:10.430 --> 38:12.630
Who was the blind one earlier,

38:12.650 --> 38:14.040
making up stories about the groom,

38:14.040 --> 38:16.400
saying he was some ugly cripple?

38:16.430 --> 38:18.310
Wasn't it you, Granny Kang?

38:17.050 --> 38:26.390
♪ Giggling, she melts into the throng
with trails of scents ♪

38:19.920 --> 38:22.220
With my years of matchmaking experience,

38:22.220 --> 38:25.120
with those looks,
not only is Song Yan far behind,

38:25.220 --> 38:26.560
in our entire Lin'an Town—

38:26.560 --> 38:28.480
no, in the whole Qingping County—
you can't find another.

38:27.680 --> 38:32.210
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

38:28.510 --> 38:29.230
Exactly.

38:32.260 --> 38:37.160
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

38:32.770 --> 38:34.860
I'm asking you. Will you take it or not?

38:34.860 --> 38:35.380
I...

38:37.770 --> 38:39.840
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

38:38.260 --> 38:38.980
Will.

38:40.410 --> 38:43.230
♪ I find her there ♪

38:43.740 --> 38:48.230
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

38:45.960 --> 38:46.850
We'll take it.

38:47.080 --> 38:48.310
Wait, what are you taking?

38:48.310 --> 38:49.450
I was asking you to take my token,

38:49.450 --> 38:51.180
not to take each other's hands.

38:57.040 --> 38:58.500
One shouldn't be too kind.

38:58.850 --> 39:00.710
Aside from keeping this ingrate,

39:00.710 --> 39:03.510
you didn't keep anything else
that bites, did you?

39:05.970 --> 39:07.570
I've raised many livestock.

39:08.170 --> 39:09.760
The only one that bites the hand
that feeds it

39:09.760 --> 39:10.870
is this one.

39:17.910 --> 39:18.840
Thank you,

39:19.470 --> 39:22.330
for having eyes but failing to
recognize a true gem.

39:23.200 --> 39:23.940
Fan Changyu.

39:24.160 --> 39:25.990
I'll assume you're blinded by lust
and confused for a moment.

39:25.990 --> 39:27.520
I won't hold it against you.

39:27.660 --> 39:29.170
I'll ask you one last time.

39:30.410 --> 39:31.610
Are you willing to...

39:35.050 --> 39:35.580
You...

39:39.360 --> 39:39.890
Let's go.

39:41.410 --> 39:42.300
Very well.

39:42.770 --> 39:43.870
Listen!

39:44.140 --> 39:45.740
You will regret this one day!

39:50.530 --> 39:51.140
You all...

39:53.110 --> 39:54.300
Fan Changyu, Yan Zheng,

39:54.300 --> 39:55.720
don't get too smug!

39:55.740 --> 39:57.290
When I place first in the imperial exams,

39:57.290 --> 39:58.730
I'll make you pay!

40:11.100 --> 40:13.150
Bow to the parents.

40:14.360 --> 40:15.150
Bow!

40:18.350 --> 40:22.860
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

40:25.190 --> 40:26.790
Share the sacrificial meat.

40:26.930 --> 40:29.570
Share weal and woe from now on,

40:29.600 --> 40:31.260
and never leave each other.

40:45.880 --> 40:47.430
Have a drink together.

40:50.870 --> 40:52.530
Perform the gargling ritual.

40:52.630 --> 40:54.670
Treat each other with respect.

40:57.980 --> 40:59.790
Drink the nuptial wine.

40:59.840 --> 41:01.720
As the sweet wine blends,

41:01.740 --> 41:04.300
may the couple live in harmony forever.

41:15.830 --> 41:17.700
-Wonderful!
-Excellent!

41:17.720 --> 41:20.410
-Wonderful!
-Excellent!

41:21.090 --> 41:22.320
Wonderful!

41:24.280 --> 41:26.200
Bride and broom bow to each other,

41:42.920 --> 41:45.110
and the ceremony is completed.

41:45.670 --> 41:49.070
Wonderful!

41:49.700 --> 41:51.130
-Great!
-Excellent!

41:53.990 --> 41:57.170
The matrilocal husband must change
his surname according to tradition.

41:57.170 --> 41:57.810
No need.

41:58.460 --> 42:00.620
My husband doesn't need to
change his surname.

42:00.620 --> 42:01.550
He'll keep the name Yan Zheng.

42:01.550 --> 42:02.750
It sounds quite nice.

42:03.990 --> 42:05.690
If you have children,

42:05.950 --> 42:08.010
they must take the mother's surname.

42:08.190 --> 42:09.610
Well, no need for that either.

42:09.610 --> 42:11.030
We'll have a couple of children

42:11.030 --> 42:12.290
and use both surnames.

42:16.360 --> 42:17.190
Keep reading.

42:17.190 --> 42:18.590
The most important part:

42:19.490 --> 42:22.540
the matrilocal husband must remember
that women are superior to men.

42:22.540 --> 42:24.450
The wife is the head of the household,

42:24.450 --> 42:25.630
-and you must follow your wife in everything...
-No need.

42:25.630 --> 42:27.470
To ensure marital harmony!

42:27.800 --> 42:29.800
-Great!
-No, no, no need.

42:31.030 --> 42:32.190
From now on,

42:32.220 --> 42:34.040
I will obey you in everything

42:34.630 --> 42:35.960
without fail, darling.

42:38.360 --> 42:39.550
In the future,

42:40.170 --> 42:41.400
we will discuss everything

42:41.400 --> 42:43.040
and make decisions together.

42:43.040 --> 42:43.610
Okay.

42:48.110 --> 42:49.580
What are you waiting for?

42:49.600 --> 42:50.920
To the bridal chamber!

42:52.760 --> 42:53.400
Come on.

42:53.420 --> 42:54.130
Yan Zheng.

42:55.030 --> 42:55.960
Go on, Yan Zheng.

42:58.790 --> 43:01.760
The bride is here to propose a toast.

43:02.070 --> 43:04.070
Thank you.

43:04.070 --> 43:05.550
Thank you, everyone.

43:05.550 --> 43:06.610
Congratulations.

43:08.920 --> 43:11.270
The bride is here to propose a toast.

43:11.300 --> 43:12.900
Changyu, congratulations.

43:13.410 --> 43:15.300
Everyone worked hard today.

43:15.330 --> 43:17.190
Please enjoy the food and drinks.

43:17.800 --> 43:19.130
-To the bride.
-Come on.

43:20.400 --> 43:21.260
Come on.

43:56.760 --> 43:58.890
[Wound Healing Elixir]

44:05.030 --> 44:06.690
Everyone, enjoy yourselves.

44:07.840 --> 44:08.640
Changyu.

44:09.220 --> 44:10.010
Changyu.

44:10.700 --> 44:11.600
Mr. Wang?

44:12.110 --> 44:12.800
Forgive me.

44:12.980 --> 44:13.770
I'm late.

44:13.850 --> 44:15.170
What took you so long?

44:15.970 --> 44:16.500
Changyu.

44:17.040 --> 44:19.500
I came late.
I'll have a penalty drink first.

44:21.710 --> 44:22.550
Come on.

44:24.000 --> 44:24.810
Changyu.

44:25.670 --> 44:26.750
These days,

44:27.140 --> 44:28.600
you've been through a lot.

44:28.970 --> 44:30.420
I've seen it all.

44:30.840 --> 44:32.340
Your father and I were old friends.

44:32.340 --> 44:33.420
From now on,

44:33.980 --> 44:35.700
treat me as half a relative.

44:36.730 --> 44:38.430
And Zhao can be the other half.

44:41.570 --> 44:43.840
Changyu, I only wish you

44:44.150 --> 44:46.530
a life that gets sweeter by the day,

44:46.670 --> 44:48.650
a path that grows ever wider,

44:48.690 --> 44:49.690
marital harmony,

44:49.800 --> 44:50.670
and a long life of love together.

44:50.670 --> 44:51.320
Well said!

44:51.440 --> 44:52.570
Thank you, Mr. Wang.

44:52.760 --> 44:53.800
Come on. Cheers.

45:05.090 --> 45:06.560
Thank you all for today.

45:07.080 --> 45:08.370
Don't mention it.

45:08.400 --> 45:09.820
Look. How beautiful.

45:09.840 --> 45:10.880
Changyu, you've had a long day.

45:10.880 --> 45:12.020
Go back and rest early.

45:12.020 --> 45:12.500
Okay.

45:12.530 --> 45:13.190
Get home safe.

45:13.190 --> 45:14.360
Congratulations, Changyu.

45:14.360 --> 45:15.950
-How pretty.
-Rest early.

45:15.970 --> 45:16.940
Rest early.

45:27.170 --> 45:28.230
What are you doing?

45:28.670 --> 45:29.550
I'm going to wash the dishes.

45:29.550 --> 45:30.190
Hold on.

45:31.130 --> 45:33.220
You don't need to wash them.

45:35.600 --> 45:37.280
[Intimacy Instruction Drawings]

45:42.040 --> 45:43.150
I won't need this.

45:43.180 --> 45:44.900
He's injured so badly. We won't need this.

45:44.900 --> 45:46.660
You'll need it sooner or later.

45:46.760 --> 45:48.170
Come on, go back to the bridal chamber.

45:48.170 --> 45:49.540
I still need to help you with the dishes.

45:49.540 --> 45:50.870
No need. Hurry up and go.

45:51.430 --> 45:53.290
Don't stand here in my way. Hurry.

45:57.170 --> 45:58.440
Changyu! Changyu!

45:58.470 --> 45:59.870
Hurry up and go upstairs.

45:59.920 --> 46:02.810
Every moment of the wedding night
is precious.

46:07.970 --> 46:08.950
Alright, alright.

46:08.950 --> 46:10.170
Let's go, let's go.

46:17.330 --> 46:17.820
Wait.

46:22.090 --> 46:23.050
I'm sorry.

46:26.130 --> 46:27.120
I'm used to living alone.

46:27.120 --> 46:28.590
I keep forgetting
there's a man in the house.
